Argu
=============

Voor een betere mening

Development
===========
Setting up
--------------
1. Clone the repo `git clone git@bitbucket.org:arguweb/argu.git`
2. Install the gems `bundle install`
3. Set up the db `rake db:setup`
4. Start the server `rails s`

Epics
------------
Epics should be added to the environment files in `config/environments`. They go in the `config.epics` hash under their epic name. When a feature is ready, it can be set to true to be shown in the respective environment, so in test/production it should be off (`false`) by default.

Enviroment variables
----------------------------
Key / Environment variable                                            |  Use                                                                                                                            |   Default
-------------------------------------------------------------------   |  -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------  |  ----------------------------
`HOSTNAME`                                                            |  The hostname used in url helpers, mailers, session store, etc                                                                  |  P: argu.nl T: logos.argu.nl D: local.host
`LOG_LEVEL`                                                           |  The log level of rails, duh.                                                                                                   |  P: info  T: debug D: debug
`GOOGLE_STORAGE_ACCESS_KEY_ID`                                        |  The access key for image uploads to GG storage                                                                                 |  -
`GOOGLE_STORAGE_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY`                                    |  The access secret for image uploads GG storage                                                                                 |  -
`SECRET_TOKEN`                                                        |  Cookie secret token                                                                                                            |  -


